title: [Reim Fortress, Western Parapet]
[Reim Fortress, West Parapet]
description: Pools of black liquid have accumulated along the floor beneath a massive black wooden bench that is filled with a thick, dark, bubbling liquid.  A blazing fire sits beneath the bench to keep its contents boiling, and doubles to provide warmth to those who gather in this roofless chamber.

Pools of black liquid have accumulated along the floor beneath a massive black iron cauldron that is filled with a thick, dark, bubbling liquid.  A blazing fire sits beneath the cauldron to keep its contents boiling, and doubles to provide warmth to those who gather in this roofless chamber.
